Class BranchesInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.conqat.engine.service.shared.data.BranchesInfo

  • public class BranchesInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Transport class for the branches of a project. This class is used for communication with IDE clients (via the @link org.conqat.engine.service.shared.client.IdeServiceClient, special care has to be taken when changing its signature!
